'''Broaden Media Academy''' (or '''BMA''') is a [[film]]/[[video]] [[post production]] training facility in [[Taipei]], [[Taiwan]]. BMA's faculty include award-winning professionals and [[Apple Computer|Apple]]-certified trainers.  BMA offers courses on many industry standard software packages, including ''[[Avid Technology|Avid]]'', ''[[Final Cut Pro]]'', ''[[Apple Motion|Motion]]'', ''[[DVD Studio Pro]]'', ''[[Pro Tools]]'' and ''[[Shake (software)|Shake]]''.

