'''Dan Meyer''' (born April 7, 1957) is an American [[sword swallowing|sword swallower]], multiple [[Guinness World Records|Guinness World record]] holder in [[Sword swallowing|sword swallowing]], a global [[TED (conference)|TEDx]] speaker, and the recipient of the 2007 [[Ig Nobel Prize]] in Medicine. Meyer was one among the Top 50 finalists on [[America's Got Talent]] Season 3 (2008), and returned to compete on [[America's Got Talent]] Season 11 (2016), and on [[La France a un incroyable talent|France's Got Talent]] in 2017. He is the president of Sword Swallowers Association International (SSAI). Meyer has also made many other television and film appearances.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/will-season-4-american-horror-story-have-sword-swallowing-pro-dan-meyer-says-stunt-too-1568210|title=Will Season 4 Of ‘American Horror Story’ Have Sword Swallowing? Pro Dan Meyer Says Stunt Is Too Dangerous, Even For ‘Freak Show’|work=ibtimes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://attractionsmagazine.com/ripleys-celebrates-10th-sword-swallowers-day/|title=Ripley’s Believe It or Not celebrates 10th annual World Sword Swallowers Day|website=attractionsmagazine.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bransontrilakesnews.com/news_free/article_d1377354-e7e6-11e6-93da-8bbef55d0fec.html|title=‘Hot Winter’ thrills; Sword Swallowers|work=bransontrilakesnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://2paragraphs.com/2016/06/agt-sword-swallower-dan-meyer-helped-by-worlds-shortest-man-22/|title=AGT: Sword Swallower Dan Meyer Helped By World’s Shortest Man (22")|work=2paragraphs}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gizmodo.com/overeating-at-the-super-bowl-is-bad-worlds-least-surpr-1791973282|title=Overeating at the Super Bowl Is Bad, World's Least Surprising Study Finds|work=gizmodo.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3721173/sword-swallowing-world-sword-swallowers-day/|title=5 Penetrating Facts About Sword Swallowing|work=time.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/dan-meter-swallows-sword-pulls-car-ripleys-baltimore-sword-swallowers-day-2013_n_2754156|title=Dan Meyer Swallows Sword While Pulling Car At Ripley's Baltimore On Sword Swallowers Day 2013|work=huffingtonpost.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/thomas-p-connelly-dds/sword-swallowing_b_1877673.html|title=Oral Hygiene Habits of the Interesting: America’s Got Talent Sword Swallower Dan Meyer|work=huffingtonpost.com}}</ref>
