==North America's Strongest Man== {{Infobox sport tournament |year = 2011 |name = North America's Strongest Man |image = |location = various locations, [[North America]] |establishment = 1992 |format = Multi-event competition |purse = |month_played = <!--Use if still played--> |final_year= <!--Use if no longer played--> |current_champion = {{flagicon|Canada}} [[Christian Savoie]] |final_champion = <!--Use if no longer played--> }}
'''North America's Strongest Man''' is an annual [[Strongman (strength athlete)|strongman]] competition consisting of athletes from both United States and Canada. The event was established in 1992.<ref name=autogenerated1 />
